movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Effects 10 Costumes 9 Acting 3 Script 2
review: It's a shame that with all the resources available this highly enjoyable super-film has to include a number of the worst lines and lamest deliveries I've seen in any major production of the last few years.  I have no trouble enjoying mindless entertainments and I love special effects, but somebody should have said something to Lucas... I was also put off by what I took to be caricatures of a number of Earth's minority groups.
